programme.title: Cucu Atuk
programme.desc: Pak Zubir menjaga cucunya, Aiman yang menjadi yatim piatu apabila kedua ibu bapanya meninggal dunia akibat kemalangan. Bapa Aiman seorang usahawan berjaya dan telah mewasiatkan harta yang banyak kepada Aiman. Pak Ngah dan Mak Ngahnya berniat jahat untuk membolot harta tersebut. Niat mereka didorong apabila Juwita meminjam wang daripada Ah Long dan gagal melunaskan pinjaman.

programme.title: Anggun Mikayla Ep1
programme.desc: Perjalanan hidup Mikayla sentiasa bersimpang-siur dengan dugaan sejak dia mencelikkan mata birunya ke dunia. Status kelahirannya membuatkan dia seringkali menerima cacian penduduk kampung dan menjadi mangsa buli semasa kecil. Mekap adalah cara Mikayla menidakkan kewujudannya sendiri. Dia berselindung di sebalik rambut palsu hitam untuk menyorokkan rambut auburnnya serta mengenakan pelbagai jenis mekap untuk menggelapkan warna kulit kerana keinginannya untuk tampak Melayu. Siang, Mikayla bekerja sebagai jurumekap artis dan apabila malam tiba, dia menjelma sebagai pontianak. Pertemuan Mikayla dengan Idriz dalam satu insiden lucu telah mencipta satu hubungan aneh yang tidak bernama. Dalam diam, Idriz menyimpan rasa tetapi keinginannya terbatas kerana tanggungjawabnya pada keluarga. Jurugambar yang bekerja bersamanya, Asif yang suka mengusik Mikayla mulai tersedar yang usikannya sudah bertukar menjadi perasaan sebenar. Tetapi, dia terlajak memikat pelakon popular bernama Andria, sebelum tersedar tentang perasaannya terhadap Mikayla. Sedang Mikayla dalam keadaan celaru, lelaki dari masa silamnya, Aidan pula muncul kembali, menagih kemaafan kerana meninggalkan parut panjang di dahinya. Aidan yang kini sudah bergelar pelakon popular cuba memadamkan kenangan sakit mereka demi merebut hati yang dirinduinya itu. Tetapi, impian Mikayla hanya satu, berhadapan dengan masa silamnya dan mencantas kebencian mama. Cinta bukan destinasi yang diimpi. Namun, hatinya terus menjadi buruan oleh tiga orang lelaki.

programme.desc: Rian beri Adif 2 bulan untuk berubah demi Farhan. Jika tiada perubahan, Adif harus pulangkan harta, batalkan kes mahkamah, dan Farhan tinggal bersama Rian. Adif terpaksa setuju dan tandatangan perjanjian. Rian gembira dan menghentikan Adif dari memasuki bilik, menyuruhnya tidur di tempat lain. Afeeq minta penjelasan tentang Adif tinggal di rumah Rian. Rian cakap itu keputusan papa. Afeeq tidak suka dan Rian jamin dia tidak akan terpedaya dengan Adif lagi. Afeeq kena pergi ke mahkamah. programme.title: Tayangan Perdana Din Tiger
programme.desc: Din Tiger seorang pakar dalam mengendali sindiket jenayah terbesar, kini tumpas di tangan pihak berkuasa. Disebabkan itu, Din terpaksa berhadapan dengan liku-liku hidup. Cerita ini membawakan pelbagai pelakon yang mengerunkan dan padat dengan emosi gerun, dibintangi oleh Datuk Aaron Aziz, Dato Afdlin Shauki, Datin Nina Juren, Adam Corrie dan Mia Sara Shauki. Saksikan Din Tiger dalam membanteras sindiket scam yang berleluasa di sekitar Malaysia ini.

programme.title: Terowong Ep2
programme.desc: "Curang" ianya memaparkan Datuk Johan bermimpi diganggu roh seorang perempuan dalam sebuah terowong. Datuk Johan merasa itu petunjuk bahawa isterinya, Sabrina curang dan merancang untuk membunuhnya. Datuk Johan telah meminta Taha menjaga isterinya semasa bercuti di Bali. Datuk Johan mengsyaki isterinya memang ada hubungan sulit dengan Taha selama ini. Datuk Johan telah membuat wasiat baru yang tidak menamakan isterinya mendapat hak sebahagian dari hartanya. Sabrina mendapat maklumat mengenai Datuk melalui peguam syarie dan pada masa yang sama Datuk juga menggunakan Taha untuk mengintip pergerkan isterinya. Datuk Johan bermimpi lagi dia dibunuh oleh isterinya, walau bagaimanapun Datuk telah merancang hendak membunuh isterinya terlebih dahulu. Datuk Johan bersemuka dengan Taha dan isterinya untuk menyelesaikan kemelut yang sedang dihadapinya, namun Datuk Johan telah tertembak Taha dan mati serta merta kerana hendak mempertahankan Sabrina. Sebelum sempat Sabrina menjelaskan hubungan beliau dengan Taha, Sabrina telah mati ditembak oleh Datuk Johan. Datuk Johan telah membuang kedua-dua mayat tersebut di sebuah kawasan belukar. Setelah Datuk Johan pergi ke rumah buruk tersebut barulah beliau mendapat tahu bahawa Sabrina sedang merancang untuk menyambut hari jadinya bersama-sama anak yatim dan akhirnya Datuk Johan mendapat tahu bahawa isterinya adalah orang yang baik. Oleh kerana syak wasangka serta cemburu yang keterlaluan Datuk Johan telah membunuh kedua-dua adik beradik tersebut tanpa usul periksa dan akhirnya Datuk Johan juga meninggal dunia akibat dicekik oleh hantu isterinya

programme.title: Terowong Ep3
programme.desc: Bertajuk "Penunggu" memaparkan sebuah lagi cerita seram yang berlatar belakangkan Terowong. Ianya mengisahkan seorang lelaki Amin bertemu dan di ganggu seorang wanita tua (penunggu terowong) yang menakutkan di dalam terowong. Dia mengigau diganggu perempuan tua (Penunggu) . Suatu hari ibunya terjumpa sehelai baju berdarah di dalam biliknya. Amin telah merayu kepada nenek tua (penunggu) itu supaya tidak mengganggunya lagi. Nenek (penunggu) itu berkata bahawa itu adalah tempatnya dan tidak sabar menunggu Amin. Amin tidak tidur selama seminggu kerana takut di ganggu oleh penunggu tersebut dan tubuhnya menjadi tidak terurus, busuk dan pucat. Suatu hari nenek itu menjelma dihadapan ibunya dan mengatakan akan mengambil Amin. Penunggu itu sayangkan Amin dan ibunya berkeras untuk menolong Amir walaupun Amir tidak mahu ibunya mendapatkan bantuan khidmat bomoh. Jin (penunggu) itu memarahi ibu Amin kerana mengganggunya dengan memanggil bomoh. Penunggu tersebut juga mengganggu Nadia kekasih Amin serta melarangnya mendekati Amin. Suatu hari ibu dan tunang Amin menjumpai Amin mati dilanggar kereta di dalam terowong itu. Nenek itu membawa Amin pergi dari terowong tersebut dengan memimpinya.

programme.title: Terowong Ep4
programme.desc: Bertajuk 'Diari' mengisahkan seorang pelajar bernama Maya dalam keadaan sedih berseorangan dan berkata-kata pada diri sendiri, mengapa semua orang membencinya. Semasa Maya sedang bercakap-cakap bersendirian di dalam terowong tersebut, ada sebuah diari telah berkata-kata dengannya dan berjanji akan menolongnya. Maya yang berdendam dengan Yana dan semua itu tercatat didalam diarinya. Maya sudah berjanji dengan puaka yang berada di dalam terowong tersebut, bahawa dia akan memberikan atau menhadiahkan seorang mangsa sebagai habuan (makanan) kepada puaka tersebut kerana menolongnya menjadi cantik. Maya mahu membalas dendam terhadap Yana dan meminta pertolongan dengan dairi berpuaka. Hantu yang menjadi kawan Maya juga memusuhi Yana dan Maya telah berubah menjadi lebih cantik dan sedikit sombong. Kawan-kawan Yana telah meninggalkan Yana untuk berkawan dengan Maya. Kawan Mustafa, Yus berkata bahawa Maya itu berkawan dengan syaitan dan serta menasihatkan Mustafa supaya menjaga dirinya agar tidak menjadi mangsa bunuh Maya. Yus telah menjadi mangsa kedua hantu tersebut, setelah Maya berdendam dan marah terhadap Yus. Setelah Maya terlihat Mustafa berdua-dua dalam sebuah restoran dan Maya nampak marah kepada Mustafa. Akhirnya Mustafa telah menjadi mangsa hantu tersebut, Maya telah pulangkan semula diari itu kepada hantu atau penunggu terowong tersebut kerana kecewa dan puaka itu telah membunuh kekasihnya Mustafa. Pada masa yang sama Yana pula telah mengambil alih menjaga 'diari' puaka tersebut

programme.title: Terowong Ep5
programme.desc: Bertajuk "Rasuah" memaparkan seorang lelaki bernama Imran bermimpi berada di dalam sebuah terowong dan diganggu lembaga setiap malam kerana bimbang akan keselamatan isterinya. Dipaparkan Imran dan Latif rakan setugas yang sedang menguruskan kes sebidang tanah dengan menaikkan nilai tanah kerana berkehendakkan duit rasuah. Isterinya suka berbelanja dengan mewah serta mempunyai hubungan sulit dengan rakan baiknya. Pada suatu malam beliau bermimpi ternampak hantu pocong dalam keretanya serta menakutkannya. Imran juga ternampak beberapa lembaga yang menyerupainya sedang mengejarnya. Mereka memberi amaran kepada Imran supaya jangan membuat sesuatu perkara yang akan menyusahkan orang lain. Imran juga bermimpi seorang bomoh mahu menolongnya dan Imran menjadi tidak tentu arah bila teringat akan mimpi tersebut. Bomoh itu telah menolong Imran dan isterinya tetapi dengan syarat mereka disuruh mandi bunga. Imran mendapat komisen atas urusan jual tanah itu dan Imran masih diganggu lagi dengan mimpi-mimpi ngeri. Bomoh itu menjelma dihadapan Imran serta mengatakan beliau mesti berani menanggung segala perbuatan rasuahnya. Imran terserempak dengan kawannya berdua-duaan dengan isterinya dan Imran tidak dapat mengawal perasaan marahnya terhadap isterinya dan membunuhnya dengan mencekik serta tidak sengaja. Imran pula mati di dalam terowong itu dan diangkat oleh lembaga hitam tersebut. Kawannya Latif pula mengalami mimpi ngeri yang sama seperti yang dialami oleh Imran.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep4
programme.desc: Hariz yakin Budi ada kena mengena kerana Budi ada masa dia bertengkar dengan Andy, Hariz tahu Budi adalah peminatnya, mungkin peminat ini bunuh mereka yang cuba sakiti Hariz.

Diganggu oleh kuasa jahat yang mengepungnya, Sam mengalami mimpi ngeri apabila syaitan dari masa lalunya enggan terus dikebumikan lagi.

programme.title: Kapsul
programme.desc: Kapsul masa wawasan 2020 yang ditanam oleh Tun Dr. Mahathir Mohamad telah dicuri dan membawa Zohri kembali ke masa lalu. Zohri kini terperangkap di tengah-tengah pergolakan bangsa Melayu untuk mencapai kemerdekaan dan membawa bangsa Melayu keluar dari belenggu kemiskinan. Zohri melihat dan merasai sendiri erti perjuangan umatnya yang tidak pernah dibayangkannya selama ini. Dia lihat, dia rasa dan kini dia mula faham betapa peritnya liku-liku sejarah negara dan bangsa. Perjalanan Zohri berterusan dari satu zaman ke satu zaman dan tiada siapa yang dapat mengembalikannya ke zamannya melainkan dirinya sendiri.

programme.desc: Ray ialah ketua geng mencuri kereta mewah, dan terlibat dalam kelab petarungan bawah tanah. Dia tidak mempunyai hubungan yang baik dengan keluarganya, tetapi apabila abangnya Remy dan isteri Remy meninggal dunia dalam satu kemalangan yang tragis, Ray terkejut kerana abangnya telah menyatakan niatnya dalam wasiat dan telah memilih Ray untuk menjadi penjaganya. dua orang anak - Arisha dan Aidil.

programme.desc: Jalan Puncak Alam mengisahkan seorang pelajar UiTM bernama Azizi yang terpaksa melalui jalan sunyi itu pada lewat malam untuk pulang ke rumah selepas bekerja di kampus. Dalam perjalanan, motosikal yang ditunggang Azizi tiba-tiba kehabisan minyak. Azizi kemudian menghubungi Hanif untuk meminta bantuan. Hanif segera menuju ke tempat motosikal Azizi rosak dan dari situ, mereka diganggu oleh makhluk halus. Apabila Hanif dan Azizi melihat keadaan sekeliling, hampir semuanya telah selesai, namun pertemuan mereka dengan seorang pemancing telah membuka satu perkara yang tidak masuk akal.

programme.title: Wangi
programme.desc: Nor dan suaminya, Khuzairi tinggal di sebuah banglo bersama dua anak mereka. Selepas melahirkan anak kedua, Nor pulang ke rumah dan ibunya datang untuk menjaganya. Dia perasan bahawa pembantu rumahnya, Bella telah hilang. Bella seperti adik kepada Nor dan dia tinggal bersama mereka. Suaminya mengatakan bahawa Bella telah kembali ke Amsterdam untuk berkahwin. Nor mengesyaki dan tidak lama kemudian anak-anaknya mula mempunyai kelakuan luar biasa. Anak pertama mereka suka bercakap dengan dirinya sendiri dan tidur di tempat yang rawak; suaminya menyembunyikan rahsia manakala seorang wanita tua sentiasa memberi amaran kepada Nor. Tanpa disedari oleh Nor, Bella yang hilang mungkin sedang mengintai di sudut gelap banglo itu.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep1
programme.desc: Din Tiger mengendalikan sindiket scammer yang terbesar bersama Big Boss Mario. Din memutuskan untuk meninggalkan dunia scammer demi memberi tumpuan kepada isterinya, anaknya. Keputusan beraninya membuatkan Big Boss Mario kecewa, tetapi dia tetap menghormati pilihan Din. Namun terdapat udang disebalik batu.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep1
programme.desc: Uzair dan Madi adalah musuh sekolah. Apabila Madi menghina kawannya Suresh, Uzair menyerang Madi. Madi membalas dengan menyerang rakan-rakan Uzair. Pidottrauma dengan serangan Madi tetapi Uzair cuba untuk menenangkan keadaan. Namun, apabila Madi menyedari bahawa CIkgu Sofi mempunyai sifatlemah lembut terhadap Uzair, Madi menyerang dan menyakiti Cikgu Sofi.

programme.title: The Beast
programme.desc: Dalam kisah pahit ini berdasarkan peristiwa sebenar, seorang pengedar dadah di Long Island mendapati dirinya kesusahan apabila salah seorang askarnya menganggu hubungan dengan gangster Serbia yang kejam. Apabila hutang jatuh ke bahunya dia terpaksa mengambil langkah drastik

programme.title: Ong Bak 2
programme.desc: Berlatarkan Thailand abad ke-15, filem ini berkisarkan Tien, anak kepada seorang bangsawan yang dibunuh. Ditawan dan dijual sebagai hamba, Tien diselamatkan daripada kematian oleh Chernang, ketua Pha Beek Khrut, sekumpulan artis mempertahankan diri yang pakar dalam pelbagai gaya tempur Asia.

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: Barajiwa Ep1
programme.desc: Uzair dan Madi adalah musuh sekolah. Apabila Madi menghina kawannya Suresh, Uzair menyerang Madi. Madi membalas dengan menyerang rakan-rakan Uzair. Pidottrauma dengan serangan Madi tetapi Uzair cuba untuk menenangkan keadaan. Namun, apabila Madi menyedari bahawa CIkgu Sofi mempunyai sifatlemah lembut terhadap Uzair, Madi menyerang dan menyakiti Cikgu Sofi.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep1
programme.desc: Din Tiger mengendalikan sindiket scammer yang terbesar bersama Big Boss Mario. Din memutuskan untuk meninggalkan dunia scammer demi memberi tumpuan kepada isterinya, anaknya. Keputusan beraninya membuatkan Big Boss Mario kecewa, tetapi dia tetap menghormati pilihan Din. Namun terdapat udang disebalik batu.

programme.title: The Beast
programme.desc: Dalam kisah pahit ini berdasarkan peristiwa sebenar, seorang pengedar dadah di Long Island mendapati dirinya kesusahan apabila salah seorang askarnya menganggu hubungan dengan gangster Serbia yang kejam. Apabila hutang jatuh ke bahunya dia terpaksa mengambil langkah drastik

programme.title: Bini-bini Ku Gangster
programme.desc: Manja dan Herry adalah sepasang suami isteri yang sangat romantik dan saling sayang menyayangi. Tanpa disedari oleh Herry, Manja adalah ketua kumpulan kepada sebuah geng gengster di Kuala Lumpur. Di pejabat,Herry kerap dibuli Mat Saja termasuk menyuruh Herry menggantikan tempatnya semasa ulangtahun perkahwinan Manja dan Herry yang ke2. Manja bengang lalu menghantar orang-orangnya memukul Mat Saja.

programme.title: Adnan Sempit 2
programme.desc: Mengisahkan tentang Adnan, seorang penunggang motosikal jalanan yang yatim piatu dan dijaga oleh bibinya. Di pihak lain, Nadia dilahirkan dalam keluarga yang kaya dan kini memiliki pekerjaan yang stabil. Kedua-dua individu yang berlatarbelakangkan dunia yang berbeza ini akhirnya bertemu secara kebetulan dan terjalin hubungan antara mereka.

programme.title: Bila Jodoh

Setelah mendapat restu ibunya, Indra mencari pekerjaan di bandar dengan bertemu Dato Karim rakan baik arwah bapanya. Indra diterima bekerja dan diminta untuk tinggal di rumah Dato Karim. Pada mulanya kehadiran Indra tidak disenangi Sandra, anak Dato Karim. Namun hubungan mereka semakin baik selepas Indra menyelamatkan Sandra daripada samseng jalanan. Pada masa yang sama, terdapat satu gerakan yang ingin mensabotaj projek yang sedang diuruskan syarikat Dato Karim.

programme.title: XX Ray 2
programme.desc: Bekerja sebagai saintis kadet, Tina berasa ditipu apabila Johan mendakwa dia yang mencipta mesin pelupusan laser walhal ia merupakan hasil cetusan idea dari Tina. Ingin menghalang niat jahat Johan, Tina meminta bantuan Amir. Namun, keduanya terkena pancaran laser mesin itu dalam cubaan untuk menghalang Johan dan telah dihantar ke zaman Kesultanan Melayu Melaka.

programme.title: Kau,Aku Dan Dia
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Nancy dan Syafiq yang baru tamat pengajian di universiti. Walaupun berlainan bangsa, namun mereka saling mencintai antara satu sama lain. Konflik mula berlaku apabila orang tua ingin menjodohkan mereka dengan orang lain. Syafiq kemudiannya bertemu dengan seorang gadis buta bernama Mastura yang dilanggarnya secara tidak sengaja. Semakin hari, hubungan antara Syafiq dan Mastura menjadi semakin rapat sehingga Nancy berasa tersisih.

programme.title: XX Ray
programme.desc: Obsesinya terhadap angkasa lepas telah membuatkan Amir untuk mencipta sebuah topi keledar. Topi keledar ini merupakan penemuan baru apabila ia menggunakan kuasa tahi bintang. Sesiapa sahaja yang memakainya boleh melihat menembusi apa sahaja yang mereka inginkan. Kekacauan berlaku apabila topi itu telah menyebabkan Amir bertukar menjadi halimunan.

programme.title: Tembus
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang lelaki bernama Hari yang memegang tanggungjawab besar dalam mengotakan janji agar kehidupan rumahtangganya menjadi semakin baik. Di mata masyarakat, Hari dan isterinya, Izza dianggap sebagai pasangan ideal yang sukses dalam hal rumahtangga dan kerjaya. Namun mereka diuji dengan kehilangan anak dan pelbagai rahsia terbongkar akibat terjadinya peristiwa itu.

programme.title: Azura (2012)
programme.desc: Azura, seorang gadis remaja yang gigih hadapi cabaran hidup untuk mencapai cita-citanya. Dia tinggal bersama ibu saudaranya setelah kedua ibu bapanya meninggal dunia dalam satu tragedi. Azura kemudiannya menjadi mahasiswa di sebuah universiti swasta dan menjalinkan hubungan mesra dengan Zek, seorang anak hartawan. Walau bagaimanapun, cinta mereka dihalang oleh bapa Zek dan mereka terpaksa melalui pelbagai dugaan.

programme.title: Jiran
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ramlan sekeluarga yang baru berpindah di sebuah kawasan perumahan. Namun, Ramlan melarang isteri dan anaknya Tina daripada bergaul dengan jiran-jiran mereka di situ. Ramlan sendiri beranggapan bahawa dengan berlaku sombong terhadap orang, dirinya akan dipandang mulia. Kesombongan Ramlan itu akhirnya menyusahkan dirinya sendiri apabila berlaku satu insiden yang melibatkan kehilangan Tina.

programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: Wolf Pack
programme.desc: The Wolf Pack squad led by Lao Diao, is a foreign-based team that specializes in overseas security jobs. In one of the missions, the squad discovers that a terrorist force is planning to destroy the countrys energy source. Lao Diao is now entrusted with the task of leading his squad to fight back. Can the Wolf Pack save the day?

programme.title: Black Ransom
programme.desc: Mann, an accomplished police officer, has allowed his career to wane after his wife was murdered by the mafia. However, Mann is forced to return to his former glory when he is assigned to investigate a former police inspector suspected to be kidnapping mafia bosses and demanding ransoms in exchange for their lives.

programme.title: In Broad Daylight
programme.desc: Based on a true event of a news investigative unit receiving a tip-off about the abuse of residents in an Elderly and Disabled Care Home. To expose the homes wrongdoings, reporter Kay goes undercover to expose the inhumanity and unveil the cruel truth under broad daylight.

programme.title: Just 1 Day
programme.desc: Mosaic, an urban sketcher, is suffering from ALS and wants to create some fond memories as his condition worsens. When Mosaic reunites with his old classmate Angelfish, whom he has a crush on since primary school, he asks her to fulfill his one last wish by becoming his girlfriend for just one day. Will Angelfish say yes?

programme.title: CZ12
programme.desc: Hawk leads a mercenary team to recover the bronze heads of the 12 Chinese zodiac animals, which were looted by foreigners in the 1800s. With a promise of a 10 times bonus by MP Corp if he can recover all of them, Hawk stops at nothing to accomplish the mission.

programme.title: Band Four
programme.desc: An aspiring singer of an indie band called Band Four reunites with her estranged guitarist father following the death of her mother. Together with her half-sister and her nine-year-old son, the newly reunited family come together to support each other through their love and passion for music.

programme.title: Golden Chickensss
programme.desc: Ah Kam is now a mama-san leading a team of young prostitutes to service the rich and famous, and she always aims to fulfil every clients needs. When Ah Kams ex-lover, a triad boss, encounters difficulties adapting to a new Hong Kong after his release from a long imprisonment, she helps him get back on his feet to lead a normal life.

programme.title: Enter the Fat Dragon
programme.desc: Donnie Yen plays a Hong Kong police officer who is highly skilled in martial arts but balloons to more than 200 pounds after his fianc left him. His boss can only assign simple tasks to him like escorting a criminal to Japan, but can he complete it?

programme.title: The Grand Grandmaster
programme.desc: Ma Fei Lung, a Chinese martial arts grandmaster, lost everything after he is floored by a former female boxing champion, Chan Tsang. The relevant video was posted on social media and he became the laughing stock of everyone. To reclaim his reputation, Fei Lung challenges Chan Tsang to a rematch. Who will be the winner?

programme.title: We are Family
programme.desc: Struggling as an extra, Chi Kwong joins a rent-a-family company run by Carlos and aspiring actress Catherine, and rent themselves out as make-believe relatives. As they surrogate different families, they unravel the complexities of family relationships, forging deeper connections along the way.

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriends wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: Bodies at Rest
programme.desc: When three armed criminals barge into a morgue, a forensic doctor and his student must fight with their lives to stop the criminals from obtaining a bullet from inside a corpse that is a key piece of evidence in a deadly crime.

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: Cyber Heist
programme.desc: Hackers have caused a large-scale cyber attack, but luckily cyber security engineer Chun, manages to fend it off with his protective firewall system. To Chun's surprise, his boss is the mastermind of the attack, and when Chun gets trapped in a money laundering operation, he must fight against his boss in the cyber world to prove his innocence.

programme.title: Detective Vs. Sleuths
programme.desc: Hong Kong is rocked by a series of cold-blooded murders whose victims are runaway suspects of unsolved cases. The group of killers calls themselves The Chosen Sleuths". Former top detective Lee vows to bring the brutal killers to justice and prove himself to be the real Chosen Sleuth instead of a lunatic.

programme.title: Sex and the Beauties
programme.desc: It is said that Hong Kong is a sexy and sexual city where life is breathtakingly fast but glamorous. Fear of marriage, single & successful psychiatrist, Selina and other beauties seek for love and happy endings.

programme.title: Mr. Long
programme.desc: A Taiwanese hitman Mr. Long escapes from the triad after his assignment in Tokyo gone awry. He encounters a Taiwanese woman and her son and the three of them start a new life together. Unfortunately, Mr. Long is being pursued by the triad again

programme.title: Beyond the Dream
programme.desc: Primary school teacher Lok is a recovering schizophrenic who falls in love with a young girl he first met. As he struggles to reveal his illness, Lok has a relapse and becomes delusional. Little does he know she is a mental health counsellor who has a hidden agenda. The pair develops a relationship that is beyond their wildest dreams.

programme.title: Crypto Storm
programme.desc: ICAC investigation officer Lok sets up a special team to investigate a corruption case involving a banks top executives use of cryptocurrency to manipulate the trading market. When the banks chairman is kidnapped and kidnappers demand ransom in crypto coins, Lok connects the dots and vows to hunt down the mastermind behind both crimes.

programme.title: Reunion Dinner
programme.desc: Chao Yang and Zi Hong are soon to wed but both have not met the other's parents. When a client requests for a livestream of their reunion dinner to promote his products, it set the stage for their parents' first meeting. Estranged from his mother, Yang decides to rent a family for the dinner which results in a series of mishaps and hilarity.

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kongs Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: Lucky Star 2015
programme.desc: When a talent manager meets a guy whose voice resembles the famous comedian Stephen Chow, things starts to stir up in the show biz. "Lucky Star 2015" is a hilarious comedy starring actors from both Hong Kong and Taiwan, including Eric Tsang, Dada Chan and Wong Cho Lam.

programme.title: Lonely Eighteen
programme.desc: Set in the 1980s Hong Kong, Elaine and her best friend Ying enter the entertainment industry hoping to change their fates from poverty. Ying soon becomes a popular porn star but Elaine is lost between being her true self and an actress. When show business declines after a decade, their choices lead them to two different paths in life.

programme.title: Tristar
programme.desc: Young priest Hong disguises himself to protect Bai, a prostitute, while Detective Liu investigates her ties to a prostitution ring. Hong finds Bai a lawful job and helps her negotiate with the underworld. Meanwhile, Liu's investigation causes misunderstandings can he crack down on the gang? How will Hong manage his emotions as Bai falls for him?

programme.title: A Guilty Conscience
programme.desc: Due to the negligence of sharp-tongued barrister Adrian, his innocent client is convicted of murder and sentenced to 17 years in jail. An opportunity to appeal the case and free his client arises a few years later, but in order to right his wrong, he must fight against one of the most powerful families in Hong Kong for justice to prevail.

programme.title: A Witness out of the Blue
programme.desc: The police suspects that a jewel thief, found dead in his unit with all stolen goods missing, is killed by his gang leader. They also found the crime to be related to a jewel robbery many months ago, with the robbers involved being killed off one by one. In this complicated case, the polices only witness is a talking parrot from the crime scene.

programme.title: Mr. & Mrs. Player
programme.desc: Chinese Feng Shui master, Carson (Chapman To) was a "Natural Born Player", taking names and breaking hearts. Fate had it that he would meet his match, the hot veterinarian, Chi-Ling (Chrissie Chau). It was love at first sight but neither could stand the other's fickle nature lest the affair might have ended as soon as it began.

programme.title: City Under Siege
programme.desc: When circus clown Sunny gets transformed into a super-powered mutant, he finds himself pitted against his fellow circus performers who were altered in the same accident, and who are now using their powers to wreak havoc around the city.

programme.title: My Blue Summer
programme.desc: Zhi has been secretly in love with Nan since she met him once as a child. After graduating high school, Zhi realizes that she and Nan are in the same university, where they get to know each other by chance and become close friends. However, Zhi is still too shy to express her love for Nan. Will this long-term crush finally turn into true love?

programme.title: Wolf Hiding
programme.desc: A cold-blooded killer, Chen An vows to take revenge for her sister who was killed by a crime gang. Dealing with the police and the triad at the same time, a final battle between good and evil has just begun!

programme.title: Fagara
programme.desc: After her fathers death, a Hong Kong girl discovers she has two hitherto unknown sisters, Branch and Cherry. Through taking up her late fathers hotpot restaurant, she reunites with her sisters by different mothers, and understands her father more from a different perspective, allowing her to finally resolve her long-time hard feelings with him.

programme.title: The Master Of Kung Fu
programme.desc: The famous kung fu master Wong Fei Hung teaches martial arts in Guangdong. A vicious gangster plots to harm Wongs disciples and frames him for robbery and murder. Wong has to fight against the culprit to prove his own innocence and take revenge for his disciples.

programme.title: Melody of Love
programme.desc: Three young doctors pursue three hard-to-get beauties in this romantic film set in the 70s a-go-go era. They have no idea where to start and use Rock-paper-scissor method to match themselves with the girls. The tactics and tricks they use are hilarious and they have to reshuffle their plans when nothing leads to success!

programme.title: Death Duel
programme.desc: Third Master is a renowned swordsman in the martial arts world, but the constant challenges by other swordsmen compel him to fake his death and pursue a secluded life. This does not prevent others from seeking him out to challenge him however, and he is forced to return to fight his way till the end.

programme.title: The Empress Dowager
programme.desc: Award-winning drama featuring a passionate performance by Lisa Lu, enhanced by sumptuous costumes and sets, produces a powerful, fascinating story. In five thousand years of Chinese history, there was never a more fascinating woman than the dragon lady of the Ching Dynasty, also the Empress Dowager, who was the power behind the throne for the last half of the 19th century. The vast tapestry of palace intrigues is vividly brought to the screen.

programme.title: The Golden Lion
programme.desc: The Golden Lion is a bandit with good martial arts skills and often robs from the rich to help the poor. He is ambushed and attacked by a gang one night but luckily found help from a master healer, who has to find a way to treat him while they are both being chased by the gang.

programme.title: Raw Courage
programme.desc: After the Ming Emperor is overthrown and his infant son was put in the care of the Black Dragon Society, a traitorous martial arts clan attacks the society, forcing an inexperienced pair of swordsman and swordswoman to flee with the infant. Their journey to deliver the infant to safety is filled with dangers that would require help from other allies

programme.title: Disco Bumpkins
programme.desc: This musical comedy is about how a young man Fen, along with his buddy Hamburger, finds love and success in the advertising world.

programme.title: The Pure and the Evil
programme.desc: Two teen girls, Rose and May, become close friends despite their different social backgrounds. The rich girl May moves to America but returns years later to see Rose, now a beauty queen and bar girl. Rose is immediately attracted to Fangs fianc and their relationship quickly deteriorates when Rose sets out to pursue him

programme.title: Young Vagabond
programme.desc: One of the great Kung-fu film characters is Beggar Su, a legendary Ching Dynasty figure who was also a member of the famous Ten Kwangtung Tigers. Little-known director Liu Shih-yu uses the best Kung-fu actors Shaw Studios had to offer to tell a rare, colorful, action-packed adventure, as Beggar Su and his brother train incessantly to defeat the brutally powerful thief called Centipede. The result is not only reminiscent of preeminent director Liu Chia-liangs work, but essentially an image to him as well.

programme.title: Moods Of Love
programme.desc: This Song Dynasty period piece about how far one would go for love (or lust) has two tales. The first involves a devilish magistrate who tries to tempt a Buddhist monk out of his self-professed celibacy by hiring a pretty prostitute. The second is the tragic tale of an exploited young girl who is forced to work in an unscrupulous couples brothel.

programme.title: The Thunderbolt Fist
programme.desc: A vicious Japanese judo expert wants to prove that Chinese are the sick people of Asia and sets out to sabotage and kill the best martial artists in dangerous tournaments. To save his son from this, the head of Ping Pai Boxing Institute sends him to the mountains to learn the powerful Thunderbolt Fist technique from master fighter, Red Butterfly.

programme.title: The Merry Wife
programme.desc: A 17-year old schoolgirl marries her 35-year-old teacher. Comedy ensues when they attempt to keep their relationship a secret despite being in the same school. When they discover unwanted suitors going after their other halves, jealousy threatens to expose their marriage any minute!

programme.title: Return of the Phoenix
programme.desc: An imperial minister Cheng betroths his pretty younger daughter, Ye, to his friend's son, Mu. His wife however, refuses to let Ye marry before her elder daughter Yan, who is ugly and undesirable. Yan is asked to pretend as Ye to meet Mu but scares him away. A rich guy who likes Ye meanwhile pretends as Mu to attend the wedding...

programme.title: Disciples of the 36th Chamber
programme.desc: In the finale of this trilogy, Gordon Liu reprises his famous role, Monk San Te, as he tries to protect Fang Shih Yu, an arrogant youth who gets into trouble with the Qing officials, and nearly lands Shaolin Temple into trouble too.

programme.title: The Dream of the Red Chamber
programme.desc: Adapted from the most widely read and filmed novel in Chinese history, this sumptuous version was said to be the most successful one. Loh Tihs looks, demeanour and aura in her portrayal of Lin Dai Yu has won her the epithet "Classic Beauty".

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: The 36th Chamber of Shaolin
programme.desc: Gordon Liu plays an anti-Manchu rebel who escapes to the Shaolin Temple and learns what it truly takes to become a martial arts master by challenging the 35 Shaolin Kung Fu chambers, eventually creating the 36th chamber himself.

programme.title: Forever Diamonds
programme.desc: Hua, a pretty fraud, steals a brilliant diamond ring from a shop in Hong Kong and escapes to Singapore. To smuggle the ring pass customs, Hua slips it into the pocket of a stranger, Yen, but then lost track of him. Hua finally spots Yen after searching for days and does everything to get close to him in order to take the ring back.

programme.title: Big Times for the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Ah Niu finds a bag of jewels on the street and becomes rich. It is at this time that Uncle Zhou asks him to sign a contract to marry a girl, but it turns out to be a trap for Ah Niu to sell his house. In the end, Ah Niu becomes poor again

programme.title: The Mighty One
programme.desc: Lung seeks five volumes of a renowned Kung Fu manual to gain invincibility. When he believes a martial arts school master possesses the volumes, he kills him and his daughter but leaves behind a young brother and sister. Years later, Lung loses two volumes and starts another bloody hunt but each attempt is interrupted by two mysterious warriors...

programme.title: The Female Prince
programme.desc: Hsiao's stepmother frames her fianc Lung when he refuses to forfeit their engagement and sends him to prison. To save him, Hsiao disguises as Lung to take the Imperial exam and ranks first place. Impressed by Hsiao, the Emperor weds the Princess to 'him'. When Hsiao comes clean on their wedding night, she persuades the Princess to follow a plan

programme.title: Hex Vs Witchcraft
programme.desc: A compulsive gambler with bad luck owes money to a violent gangster boss and trades his wife as down payment, causing her to leave him. As he decides to kill himself, a mysterious old man offers him a proposal to marry the ghost of his dead daughter in exchange for cash and an expensive apartment.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Ah Chiao, a village girl stranded in the city, befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are poor but happy, though Ah Chiaos fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she soon learns that money cannot buy one happiness...

programme.title: The Twin Swords
programme.desc: Gui Wu and his wife Gan Lian Zhu are the famous Twin Swords in the martial arts world. One day, they stumble upon a kidnapping plot at the Red Lotus Temple and Lian Zhu is held captive. Wu successfully escapes to find the Gan family for help, not knowing that he is sending them into an ambush by the kidnappers. Can he finally save Lian Zhu?

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung goes incognito to mix with his people and understand their needs. He encounters many strange things along the way, including being arrested and nearly beheaded. Who will save him?

programme.title: The Emperor and his Brother
programme.desc: The Emperor Qianlong is not the legitimate successor to the throne at birth, but he only learns the truth when two senior members of a subversive anti-government secret organisation contact him years later. As it happens, the chef of this organisation is Qianlongs younger brother and they must now confront each other in opposing roles

programme.title: The Deadly Duo
programme.desc: The prince of the Sung Dynasty is captured by the Chin invaders and is guarded by top martial arts masters. It is up to two powerful patriots to fight the overwhelming odds and pull off the impossible: to rescue the royal Prince and get out of the Chin stronghold alive.

programme.title: My Name Ain't Suzie
programme.desc: Young Mei Li works as a bar girl in Wanchai to make a living. When she meets Jimmy in the bar, she thinks he is her true love and falls crazily in love with him. When Jimmy has to leave, Mei Li is devastated. It is not until she encounters the triad boss Ying that she finally found someone to count on.

programme.title: Holy Flame of the Martial World
programme.desc: This internationally popular tale of a brother and sister, seeking vengeance for the death of their parents through using the mythical yin/yang Holy Flame kung-fu technique. It's an outstanding epic choreographed and co-starring lead "Venom" Kuo Chue (aka. Philip Kwok).

programme.title: Legendary Weapons of China
programme.desc: Lei Kung, the leader of the Boxer Clan in Yunnan, dissolves the clan to save his disciples before going into self-exile. The Clan sends various assassins to kill him but failed. They then assigned Kungs brother Yong to find and kill Kung, leading to a battle between the two brothers.

programme.title: Gossip Street
programme.desc: All neighbours gather to gossip in flat number 8 on the second floor of the Gossip Street apartment building! Most of the residents are common people from all walks of life and there is never a lack of laughter or sarcasm in the neighbourhood. However, when a local mobster wants to change the place into a gambling den, things get serious...

programme.title: The Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This side-splitting comedy sees naive Ah Niu headed to Hong Kong, where he is repeatedly exploited and taken advantage of, and eventually finds himself arrested and imprisoned! Can he survive difficult times and finally overcome adversity?

programme.title: The New One-Armed Swordsman
programme.desc: David Chiang plays the all-new one-armed hero - a man who chops off his right arm rather than live with dishonor. When the love of his life is kidnapped and his best friend is murdered by the evil gang, it is time to battle.

programme.title: The Mad Monk
programme.desc: The movie consists of four stories of the Mad Monk helping others, from saving a mother and daughter from crumbling walls, to helping hawkers deal with bullies, recovering stolen money for a young man and punishing a devious court official and his son.

programme.title: The Millionaire Chase
programme.desc: It's a fun and wild romp that mixes pleasure with pleasure. A nightclub owner, playboy Peter Chen Ho, has his ways with three sisters while gallivanting across Asia. Each one has a dangling relationship to save - ensuring a series of mishaps and comic moments.

programme.title: Honey Bunny And Swap Trap Ep1
programme.desc: When a gang of bad guys set a diabolical trap, Honey and Bunny team up with the other pets to thwart them.

But when the party is over, Detective Cooper now Chummy Sparklestone refuses to break character, and hes causing problems around the village!

programme.title: Dinotrux Ep22
programme.desc: Wind - A fierce windstorm traps the gang inside the garage and they have fun together all night, but once the food runs out they team up to find a way out.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep35
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Ghastly Danger of the Ghost Dentist - The pressure's on Harold and George to tell the scariest campfire story ever. Perhaps their tale of an ill-fated frontier dentist will do the trick.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep36
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Confounding Concoction of the Crooked Combotato - A fierce game of plot potato takes an unexpected twist when Melvin unleashes one of his most fiendish -- and carb-loaded -- creations yet.

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep18
programme.desc: Winkly Fest / Snow - When Pixie struggles to recreate an old tradition perfectly, the kids realize they can make their own traditions./ A story told by Chef J inspires Juniper to go in search of snow.
